The paper discusses the construction of gazetteers using Big Data technologies, specifically Hadoop, and focuses on the processing and analysis of geotagged datasets. Therefore, cs.DB (databases), cs.IR (information retrieval), and cs.DC (distributed, parallel, and cluster computing) are likely categories. Additionally, the paper discusses trust models for quality assurance, which could fall under cs.CY (computers and society) or cs.SI (social and information networks).
